## 2026-03-28 - Missing `await` on `tokenStore.getSet()` in resolver-store.ts:161
- Added `await` to the `tokenStore.getSet(setName)` call inside `loadExternal` in `resolver-store.ts`. The function was already `async` but the call was missing `await`, causing the Promise (always truthy) to skip the `!set` guard and pass `undefined` tokens downstream.
